{"tid":836982,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【🌋樓爆2018】連登樓市Avengers救世失敗？淡淡平少少就狗衝😨上源超額認購十倍","createTime":"2018-09-26T04:53:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T09:44:54.000Z","uid":43146,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3e2f70eb3e72810b2233cda4b0ea3975c8ae8a0a","tid":836982,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T04:53:33.000Z","msg":"上源收票2500票超額10倍 加推116伙 (20:58)文章日期：2018年9月25日<br />\n<br />\n萬科（香港）掃笏管上源以實呎低於1萬元推售，成功吸客，截止今晚8時，已收到近2,500票，以首張價單231伙計算，超額認購近10倍，發展商以原價加推價單第2號，合共116個單位，戶型涵蓋1房至3房，更首次推出極高層及平台單位，價單定價由543.3萬元至1065.1萬元，平均實呎13,323元，計算最高折扣16%，及1%提早付清樓價現金回贈，折實價為451.8萬至885.73萬元，折實呎價為10,171至14,549元，平均實呎11,080元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1537880511920&amp;issue=20180925\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1537880511920%26issue%3D20180925&d=1Ve4h91KlXkq42%2Ftlc1Cek%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=bc8d62e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1537880511920%26issue%3D20180925&h=56b9483a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1537880511920&amp;issue=20180925</a>"},{"pid":"1d531b3044ca5a31bf6783bcead7431cbd7e6d7c","tid":836982,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T04:57:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc2eb0b4c7b6e1aa7c2d1a3181cb5b5a6d6f8cb4","tid":836982,"uid":43146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:02:24.000Z","msg":"連登淡淡救世失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50818acb0c6c6b74c0f3c9e18b3f443a512270b1","tid":836982,"uid":164283,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bc2eb0b4c7b6e1aa7c2d1a3181cb5b5a6d6f8cb4","tid":836982,"uid":43146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T05:02:24.000Z","msg":"連登淡淡救世失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c